{"tid":196848,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵大故障　不回應出事裝置產地　明年起中國製列車取代英國貨","createTime":"2017-04-11T14:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T15:31:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02fb7c8974d0219d95050cb455f0cec410b681d7","tid":196848,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/news_4b-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fnews_4b-1.png&h=98890654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵昨晚大故障，觀塘線由九龍塘至觀塘站服務中斷兩小時，期間油麻地站亦有列車故障，導致荃灣線亦受阻近一小時。港鐵車務總監劉天成表示該公司重視事件，將深入調查，並稱觀塘線受阻主要由於固定架空電纜的裝置受損，然而，劉天成未有回應出事裝置產地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵現任行政總裁梁國權於二零一五年三月上任，翌月即向傳媒表示，港鐵近年引入的中國製列車質素不俗，表現比早年購買的英國、西班牙及韓國製列車好；此番言論惹來批評，市民紛紛指出部份中國製新列車造工差劣，鑲嵌不平；二零一一年，一列中國列車在香港試車時，由於訊號系統失靈，列車未在預定停車位置停下，列車過走（即「衝過龍」）十三米，需司機緊急煞車，險於彩虹站附近釀成嚴重事故。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵於二零一五年七月，向中國南車購入九十三列中國列車，宣佈將於二零一八年起，在市區線以中國車逐漸全面取代英製列車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/04/mtr-failure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2017%2F04%2Fmtr-failure%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=cf686779\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/04/mtr-failure/</a>"},{"pid":"2a887e76bcd2b3628f5801f231aec86d1aff67d8","tid":196848,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d95a962a559738d950fff8f6e451850854ce73","tid":196848,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a7558e268c7dae25d30b5359b0c5dd0f83ab56","tid":196848,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df3c774f9f308efaf851c68e9c3a0acffb08ca0","tid":196848,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56d711729d20638b1a5475b5cab8dfdfc796b44b","tid":196848,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"反正是用超高價錢買返來的支那貨！心照啦！"}]}